A man blew softly and the water from the tap immediately turned to ice. He grabbed the ice, broke it and filled a glass. He was different from everyone else, but no one knew who he really was. His speed was like that of lightning. He could run at incredible speeds. That day, he had come to meet his girlfriend and he didn't even have to wait. They sat in a hotel chatting. The girl wanted to test if he was really boyfriend material. Just then, some troublemakers entered the hotel. The girl began flirting with them and they laughed at her. She walked up to them and said, can you compete with my boyfriend? One of the guys walked over and he flipped the man the middle finger. The man said, I don't want any trouble. I'm a peaceful guy. But the guy jabbed his chest and shoved him down. The man fell and everyone laughed as they walked away. He was so angry that he cracked the tile beneath him. He sat there quietly. His girlfriend left, thinking he was a loser. Then he noticed time moving incredibly fast. A train was approaching, but it didn't stop. The brakes had failed. So the man jumped onto the tracks and started chasing the train at full speed. People were terrified. The man ran like a madman and reached the next station. Before the train, he stood in front of it, hands outstretched. The train hit him, but he held On to the front. The driver was shocked. The man held on, then jumped off and ran again. He reached the next station where he pulled out a water pipe and stretched it across both ends of the.

This Soviet cook was preparing a meal for his soldiers when suddenly he spotted a German tank rolling in from the distance. The moment he saw the enemy, he ducked for cover, but the tank began firing wildly without even aiming. One shell struck his field kitchen, obliterating all the food he had worked so hard to make. Seeing this, the cook completely lost it. In a fit of rage, he grabbed an axe, climbed onto the tank and began shouting as he struck it furiously. The German soldiers inside panicked, firing blindly into the air, but they couldn't see a thing outside. The cook sat right in front of the machine gun, winging his axe over and over. With the nonstop firing and heat, the gun barrel bent out of shape. Realizing someone was on top of the tank, the soldiers tried to speed up and shake him off, but the cook held on tight. Then he ripped off his apron and covered the periscope, tore his shirt sleeves and blocked the remaining viewports, leaving the crew inside completely blind. Panicking tank veered off course and crashed into a tent. The cook smashed open the hatch with his axe and climbed out. He began shouting at the top of his lungs. His heavy footsteps, the sound of his axe and his wild screams echoed together. It sounded like an entire Soviet army was charging in. Then he set a bundle of hay on fire and shoved it into the Tank smoke filled the interior. German soldiers broke down, some crying, some laughing hysterically. Then the cook yelled in broken German, bring the anti tank grenades. Hearing that, the terrified crew completely lost control and hurried to open the hatch.

The boy took a large gulp of seawater, but it only made him feel even thirstier. He looked at the dying tiger and poured all the water into its mouth. Then he cradled the tiger in his lap, quietly awaiting death. Tears streamed down his cheeks. They had been drifting on the Pacific Ocean for over 100 days. But when the boy woke up again, he found himself on a small island. He quickly climbed onto the shore and picked a fruit to eat. After filling his stomach, he ventured deeper into the island. He passed through a dense forest, where he spotted a group of meerkats surrounded by clear pools of water. The boy joyfully jumped in and swam, heart soaring with happiness. He was so thrilled to be alive that he forgot all his pain. And the tiger was even more excited. This place felt like paradise to him. Boy calmed himself down and tied his girlfriend's necklace to a tree branch. With the island offering plenty of food, he decided to stay for a while. But soon danger made him reconsider. At sunset, the meerkats rushed up into the trees as though terrified. The tiger also sensed something wrong and ran back toward the lifeboat. First, the boy didn't pay much attention and continued to play with the little animals. But as night fell, he noticed something strange. Many dead fish floated in the pools, and the once clear water had turned into strong acid. The island was Hiding a deadly secret.

The girl was eating ice cream, but to avoid getting scolded by her mom, she lied and said she was eating chicken nuggets. Then in the next moment, something unbelievable happened. The ice cream in her hand actually turned into chicken nuggets. And even the bowl of ice cream on the table transformed into leftover chicken pieces from the fridge. This was just the beginning. The girl was still trying to make sense of it. Suddenly, her phone rang. It was her best friend Lena calling. She told her that she had bumped into her ex boyfriend on the way. But Ella wasn't interested in her love story at all. So she replied, I can't talk right now. However, the very next second, her voice completely stopped. No matter how hard she tried, not a single word would come out. Then she remembered the ice cream incident and quickly texted Lena saying, I can't talk. At that exact moment, her voice returned. To check if it was true, she sent another text, I'm wearing a blue T-shirt. When she looked down, T-shirt really had turned blue. Now Ella was super excited. She texted, I'm having pizza for dinner. Right then, the fried chicken on the table turned into pizza. Next, her eyes landed on her test paper and she wrote, I got full marks on my test. Instantly, the paper with an F grade transformed into an A. Just then, her phone rang again. Lena asked, why are you sending Me? These strange messages, Ella replied. You won't believe it, I'm so happy

This man saves $500 every single day. He's been doing it relentlessly for 35 years. But the strange thing is he combs his hair with an old toothbrush. Even his mirror is nothing more than the shiny side of a nail clipper. That's not the weirdest part. Every morning, he hangs a plastic bottle in the air, pierces a few holes with a needle and bathes under the dripping water, calm as ever. Once done, he slips on his vest, puts on his headphones and begins his morning workout. But his gym is no fancy place, just a narrow staircase lined with snacks and soda cans. When he's finished, he kneels down quietly, removes his headphones and begins to pray. Yet his prayer isn't to any god. It's to a small red bag resting by the wall. His eyes are firm because without that little bag, he wouldn't survive in this endless loop. For 35 long years, that bag has been the only thing keeping him alive. When the prayer ends, he opens it. He takes out a juice box, places it carefully beside the wall, then pulls out a stack of cash and adds it to the growing mountain of money beside him. After that, he cleans the bag, folds it neatly, and his day's work is done. He leans back, opens a book and starts to read as if time itself has stopped. The old man who lives upstairs is the complete opposite. After 35 years of being Trapped here, he's lost all will to live. Now he only eats and sleeps surrounded by piles of garbage. His corner a decaying mirror of despair, a sharp contrast to the man below, who still clings to routine and to the illusion of hope.

Only through this could she cram into the slipper, gaining the chance to rival her stepsister for the prince's hand. But to capture the prince's heart, she resolved to reinvent herself utterly. Then the physician lifted a mallet, began reconstructing her nasal bridge. A scream echoed. The gory scene stunned her younger sister. Yet the mother smiled with gratification, for she was convinced this was their family's sole opportunity. With her nose in a cast post surgery, her mother immediately enrolled her in dance academy. Since marrying royalty demanded flawless physical Grace. But on the very first day, she was relegated to the back row for her appearance while her beautiful stepsister was positioned in the front line, shattering what remained of her self worth. Yet to wed the prince, she endured the grueling regiment. To her astonishment when audition results were posted, she was unexpectedly chosen, only to discover during training her mother had bribed an instructor. Her confidence collapsed anew. To console her, the mother handed over.
